            "api_nlt_to_ref": "Deuteronomy.9:1-10:22",
            "value": "%3Cdiv%20class%3D%22%20NLT%20NLT%20BibleText%20section%22%3E%3Csection%3E%3Ch2%20class%3D%22bk_ch_vs_header%22%3EDeuteronomy%209%3A1-10%3A22%2C%20NLT%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22deut_9_1%22%20bk%3D%22deut%22%20ch%3D%229%22%20vn%3D%221%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22chapter-number%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22cw%22%3EDeuteronomy%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23xA0%3B%3Cspan%20class%3D%22cw_ch%22%3E9%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22subhead%22%3EVictory%20by%20God%26%23x2019%3Bs%20Grace%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body-ch-hd%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E1%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x201C%3BListen%2C%20O%26%23xA0%3BIsrael!%20Today%20you%20are%20about%20to%20cross%20the%20Jordan%20River%20to%20take%20over%20the%20land%20belonging%20to%20nations%20much%20greater%20and%20more%20powerful%20than%20you.%20They%20live%20in%20cities%20with%20walls%20that%20reach%20to%20the%20sky!%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22deut_9_2%22%20bk%3D%22deut%22%20ch%3D%229%22%20vn%3D%222%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E2%3C%2Fspan%3EThe%20people%20are%20strong%20and%20tall%26%23x2014%3Bdescendants%20of%20the%20famous%20Anakite%20giants.%20You%26%23x2019%3Bve%20heard%20the%20saying%2C%20%26%23x2018%3BWho%20can%20stand%20up%20to%20the%20Anakites%3F%26%23x2019%3B%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22deut_9_3%22%20bk%3D%22deut%22%20ch%3D%229%22%20vn%3D%223%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E3%3C%2Fspan%3EBut%20recognize%20today%20that%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20your%20God%20is%20the%20one%20who%20will%20cross%20over%20ahead%20of%20you%20like%20a%20devouring%20fire%20to%20destroy%20them.%20He%20will%20subdue%20them%20so%20that%20you%20will%20quickly%20conquer%20them%20and%20drive%20them%20out%2C%20just%20as%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20has%20promised.%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22deut_9_4%22%20bk%3D%22deut%22%20ch%3D%229%22%20vn%3D%224%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E4%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x201C%3BAfter%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20your%20God%20has%20done%20this%20for%20you%2C%20don%26%23x2019%3Bt%20say%20in%20your%20hearts%2C%20%26%23x2018%3BThe%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20has%20given%20us%20this%20land%20because%20we%20are%20such%20good%20people!%26%23x2019%3B%20No%2C%20it%20is%20because%20of%20the%20wickedness%20of%20the%20other%20nations%20that%20he%20is%20pushing%20them%20out%20of%20your%20way.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22deut_9_5%22%20bk%3D%22deut%22%20ch%3D%229%22%20vn%3D%225%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E5%3C%2Fspan%3EIt%20is%20not%20because%20you%20are%20so%20good%20or%20have%20such%20integrity%20that%20you%20are%20about%20to%20occupy%20their%20land.%20The%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20your%20God%20will%20drive%20these%20nations%20out%20ahead%20of%20you%20only%20because%20of%20their%20wickedness%2C%20and%20to%20fulfill%20the%20oath%20he%20swore%20to%20your%20ancestors%20Abraham%2C%20Isaac%2C%20and%20Jacob.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22deut_9_6%22%20bk%3D%22deut%22%20ch%3D%229%22%20vn%3D%226%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E6%3C%2Fspan%3EYou%20must%20recognize%20that%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20your%20God%20is%20not%20giving%20you%20this%20good%20land%20because%20you%20are%20good%2C%20for%20you%20are%20not%26%23x2014%3Byou%20are%20a%20stubborn%20people.%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22deut_9_7%22%20bk%3D%22deut%22%20ch%3D%229%22%20vn%3D%227%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22subhead%22%3ERemembering%20the%20Gold%20Calf%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body-hd%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E7%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x201C%3BRemember%20and%20never%20forget%20how%20angry%20you%20made%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20your%20God%20out%20in%20the%20wilderness.%20From%20the%20day%20you%20left%20Egypt%20until%20now%2C%20you%20have%20been%20constantly%20rebelling%20against%20him.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22deut_9_8%22%20bk%3D%22deut%22%20ch%3D%229%22%20vn%3D%228%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E8%3C%2Fspan%3EEven%20at%20Mount%20Sinai%3Ca%20class%3D%22a-tn%22%3E*%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-ref%22%3E9%3A8%3C%2Fspan%3E%20Hebrew%20%3Cem%3EHoreb%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%20another%20name%20for%20Sinai.%3C%2Fspan%3E%20you%20made%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20so%20angry%20he%20was%20ready%20to%20destroy%20you.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22deut_9_9%22%20bk%3D%22deut%22%20ch%3D%229%22%20vn%3D%229%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E9%3C%2Fspan%3EThis%20happened%20when%20I%20was%20on%20the%20mountain%20receiving%20the%20tablets%20of%20stone%20inscribed%20with%20the%20words%20of%20the%20covenant%20that%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20had%20made%20with%20you.%20I%20was%20there%20for%20forty%20days%20and%20forty%20nights%2C%20and%20all%20that%20time%20I%20ate%20no%20food%20and%20drank%20no%20water.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22deut_9_10%22%20bk%3D%22deut%22%20ch%3D%229%22%20vn%3D%2210%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E10%3C%2Fspan%3EThe%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20gave%20me%20the%20two%20tablets%20on%20which%20God%20had%20written%20with%20his%20own%20finger%20all%20the%20words%20he%20had%20spoken%20to%20you%20from%20the%20heart%20of%20the%20fire%20when%20you%20were%20assembled%20at%20the%20mountain.%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22deut_9_11%22%20bk%3D%22deut%22%20ch%3D%229%22%20vn%3D%2211%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E11%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x201C%3BAt%20the%20end%20of%20the%20forty%20days%20and%20nights%2C%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20handed%20me%20the%20two%20stone%20tablets%20inscribed%20with%20the%20words%20of%20the%20covenant.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22deut_9_12%22%20bk%3D%22deut%22%20ch%3D%229%22%20vn%3D%2212%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E12%3C%2Fspan%3EThen%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20said%20to%20me%2C%20%26%23x2018%3BGet%20up!%20Go%20down%20immediately%2C%20for%20the%20people%20you%20brought%20out%20of%20Egypt%20have%20corrupted%20themselves.%20How%20quickly%20they%20have%20turned%20away%20from%20the%20way%20I%20commanded%20them%20to%20live!%20They%20have%20melted%20gold%20and%20made%20an%20idol%20for%20themselves!%26%23x2019%3B%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22deut_9_13%22%20bk%3D%22deut%22%20ch%3D%229%22%20vn%3D%2213%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E13%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x201C%3BThe%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20also%20said%20to%20me%2C%20%26%23x2018%3BI%20have%20seen%20how%20stubborn%20and%20rebellious%20these%20people%20are.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22deut_9_14%22%20bk%3D%22deut%22%20ch%3D%229%22%20vn%3D%2214%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E14%3C%2Fspan%3ELeave%20me%20alone%20so%20I%20may%20destroy%20them%20and%20erase%20their%20name%20from%20under%20heaven.%20Then%20I%20will%20make%20a%20mighty%20nation%20of%20your%20descendants%2C%20a%20nation%20larger%20and%20more%20powerful%20than%20they%20are.%26%23x2019%3B%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22deut_9_15%22%20bk%3D%22deut%22%20ch%3D%229%22%20vn%3D%2215%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E15%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x201C%3BSo%20while%20the%20mountain%20was%20blazing%20with%20fire%20I%20turned%20and%20came%20down%2C%20holding%20in%20my%20hands%20the%20two%20stone%20tablets%20inscribed%20with%20the%20terms%20of%20the%20covenant.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22deut_9_16%22%20bk%3D%22deut%22%20ch%3D%229%22%20vn%3D%2216%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E16%3C%2Fspan%3EThere%20below%20me%20I%20could%20see%20that%20you%20had%20sinned%20against%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20your%20God.%20You%20had%20melted%20gold%20and%20made%20a%20calf%20idol%20for%20yourselves.%20How%20quickly%20you%20had%20turned%20away%20from%20the%20path%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20had%20commanded%20you%20to%20follow!%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22deut_9_17%22%20bk%3D%22deut%22%20ch%3D%229%22%20vn%3D%2217%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E17%3C%2Fspan%3ESo%20I%20took%20the%20stone%20tablets%20and%20threw%20them%20to%20the%20ground%2C%20smashing%20them%20before%20your%20eyes.%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22deut_9_18%22%20bk%3D%22deut%22%20ch%3D%229%22%20vn%3D%2218%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E18%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x201C%3BThen%2C%20as%20before%2C%20I%20threw%20myself%20down%20before%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20for%20forty%20days%20and%20nights.%20I%20ate%20no%20bread%20and%20drank%20no%20water%20because%20of%20the%20great%20sin%20you%20had%20committed%20by%20doing%20what%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20hated%2C%20provoking%20him%20to%20anger.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22deut_9_19%22%20bk%3D%22deut%22%20ch%3D%229%22%20vn%3D%2219%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E19%3C%2Fspan%3EI%20feared%20that%20the%20furious%20anger%20of%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%2C%20which%20turned%20him%20against%20you%2C%20would%20drive%20him%20to%20destroy%20you.%20But%20again%20he%20listened%20to%20me.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22deut_9_20%22%20bk%3D%22deut%22%20ch%3D%229%22%20vn%3D%2220%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E20%3C%2Fspan%3EThe%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20was%20so%20angry%20with%20Aaron%20that%20he%20wanted%20to%20destroy%20him%2C%20too.%20But%20I%20prayed%20for%20Aaron%2C%20and%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20spared%20him.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22deut_9_21%22%20bk%3D%22deut%22%20ch%3D%229%22%20vn%3D%2221%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E21%3C%2Fspan%3EI%20took%20your%20sin%26%23x2014%3Bthe%20calf%20you%20had%20made%26%23x2014%3Band%20I%20melted%20it%20down%20in%20the%20fire%20and%20ground%20it%20into%20fine%20dust.%20Then%20I%20threw%20the%20dust%20into%20the%20stream%20that%20flows%20down%20the%20mountain.%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22deut_9_22%22%20bk%3D%22deut%22%20ch%3D%229%22%20vn%3D%2222%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E22%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x201C%3BYou%20also%20made%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20angry%20at%20Taberah%2C%3Ca%20class%3D%22a-tn%22%3E*%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-ref%22%3E9%3A22a%3C%2Fspan%3E%20%3Cem%3ETaberah%3C%2Fem%3E%20means%20%26%23x201C%3Bplace%20of%20burning.%26%23x201D%3B%20See%20Num%2011%3A1-3.%3C%2Fspan%3E%20Massah%2C%3Ca%20class%3D%22a-tn%22%3E*%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-ref%22%3E9%3A22b%3C%2Fspan%3E%20%3Cem%3EMassah%3C%2Fem%3E%20means%20%26%23x201C%3Bplace%20of%20testing.%26%23x201D%3B%20See%20Exod%2017%3A1-7.%3C%2Fspan%3E%20and%20Kibroth-hattaavah.%3Ca%20class%3D%22a-tn%22%3E*%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-ref%22%3E9%3A22c%3C%2Fspan%3E%20%3Cem%3EKibroth-hattaavah%3C%2Fem%3E%20means%20%26%23x201C%3Bgraves%20of%20gluttony.%26%23x201D%3B%20See%20Num%2011%3A31-34.%3C%2Fspan%3E%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22deut_9_23%22%20bk%3D%22deut%22%20ch%3D%229%22%20vn%3D%2223%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E23%3C%2Fspan%3EAnd%20at%20Kadesh-barnea%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20sent%20you%20out%20with%20this%20command%3A%20%26%23x2018%3BGo%20up%20and%20take%20over%20the%20land%20I%20have%20